  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Strengthening social cohesion and stability in slum populations</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project aims at strengthening social cohesion and stability in slum populations by addressing the root causes of inter-communal conflict in slum populations by looking at the sources of grievances and strengthening community cohesion around shared development assets in Uganda. The action will combine employment opportunities and the provision of basic local services with conflict prevention.</narrative>
  </description>
